item.title: Today was rough
item.description: Routine minor surgery. Complications coming out of anesthesia. Vet transfered her to an ER. I arrived at the ER before her but gave the nurses space to set her up to monitors. Immediately started cpr. Got a heartbeat back after 10 mins but not before she went brain dead. I wasnt informed it was that critical and took a minute to compose myself. I didnt show myself to her until midway through the cpr, but it was too late by then, she wasn’t conscious. And im distraught thinking her last thoughts were of looking for me and i wasnt there. its always been me and her against the world….it seems like the world has been winning an awful lot lately.

item.title: AP Review Finds Dozens of ICE Employees Charged With Abuse and Corruption as Agency Expands
item.description:
ICE has expanded rapidly in the past year, in staffing numbers and in reach. Officials say they have hired more than 12,000 agents in less than a year, which President Trump has deployed to at least 15 American cities. The violence ICE officers bring into these communities has been well documented: Officers have assaulted, detained, and killed protesters and suspected undocumented immigrants. https://theconversation.com/ice-immigration-tactics-are-shocking-more-americans-as-us-mexico-border-operations-move-north-273741
